{"tid":1963253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係梁耀忠黃碧雲] 支持特首加薪點名簿","createTime":"2020-04-08T04:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T06:50:01.000Z","uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48fc12b72eba380114c3c1b24946e1838d9e4628","tid":1963253,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T04:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9gKJdS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9gKJdS.jpg&h=dc8cc789&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n//【紀錄表】<br />\n林鄭月娥回應她被批評<br />\n疫情下仍獲加薪時<br />\n指這機制調整是經立法會批准的<br />\n小編尋回當日會議的投票紀錄<br />\n發現這機制調整<br />\n當時只以四票之差獲通過<br />\n民主派有五人缺席<br />\n而日前要求特首減薪的兩名建制派<br />\n當年亦支持通過機制調整//<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/263143884538149/photos/a.276896536496217/636963233822877/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F263143884538149%2Fphotos%2Fa.276896536496217%2F636963233822877%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=c4af15a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/263143884538149/photos/a.276896536496217/636963233822877/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當中缺席人士包括:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">梁耀忠、黃碧雲</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">、梁繼昌、葉建源等人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n郭家麒現時處理內會會議 拖到班建制一直開唔到會的 <br />\n依方面真係人做得幾好<br />\n但見佢當年冇出現都幾失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而其他人....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">梁耀忠、黃碧雲</span></span></strong>[b]<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\